{"type": "article", "id": 57694, "title": "一个低成本地震报警器，意在减少地震带居民的恐慌情绪｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-10-25T23:28:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 53722, "name": "Ferdinand Aichriedler"}, {"id": 53723, "name": "Patrick Krassnitzer"}, {"id": 53724, "name": "Manuel Hess"}, {"id": 28105, "name": "Philippe Malouin"}, {"id": 53725, "name": "Tiberio Lobo-Navia"}, {"id": 53726, "name": "Ameé Allsop"}, {"id": 53727, "name": "Aurore Brard"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 76, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181025230112wSsBRYGtHuFrZPMU.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Terra by Ferdinand Aichriedler, Patrick Krassnitzer and Manuel Hess</h3><p>瑞典 Umeå 设计学院的学生 Ferdinand Aichriedler、Patrick Krassnitzer 和 Manuel Hess 合力创造了一个极简的、低成本的地震警报器 Terra，目标受众是那些生活在地震带上常年受到连续地壳板块运动影响的人群。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 19.0px; font: 13.0px 'Helvetica Neue'} </style>  </p><p>设计师希望创造一个简单的警报系统，可以融入人们的家庭，即便是贫困社区的人们也负担得起，降低恐惧感。缺乏信息可能导致人们潜意识中持续存在的恐慌感。Terra 就是一种增强意识和减少易受地震影响的国家恐慌的装置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l07652r29mn\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230307ALYkBfNTw8R4MpqS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.569797\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230149qXf97PRjA6ioYF1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.489002\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230156dUIsLO5kESqb6Mi0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810252301586BUEqo8VSCN2uftb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561760\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230201d1LJzW4G0e69t75U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Line Lamp by Philippe Malouin for Zaozuo</h3><p>法国设计师 Philippe Malouin 是各大国际家具家居展览的常客，并将 W Hotels“未来设计师”，以及《Wallpaper》“最佳材质运用”等多个奖项收入囊中。最近，他为家居设计品牌造作设计了一款台灯，名叫“线灯”，是一款零频闪无极调光护眼灯。</p><p>他从“Live like a designer”发想，为满足设计师、手工艺人、工程师等各类专业人士需求。以一条回形线，让光自如旋转角度。灯管 350°旋转，角度范围内任意可调，扩大光线可照射范围，满足不同光照需求，轻松让光线投向需位置。灯臂前后 45°调整范围，调整不同高度，拉近与桌面距离，让光源更集中，为精细工作提供更清晰照明。</p><p>亮度稳定无频闪、无眩光，光线均匀，有助于缓解眼疲劳。近似自然光的暖白光，适配工作、阅读多种模式。售价 380 元，<a href=\"https://www.zaozuo.com/item/300366\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018102523035760zt73cTU1S98HXQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230357rxL7zXiWChgRZQaI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230359owaCs4tWEe6Y032D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230400wkPic13mTgNOdGru.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230401qM0T3oDFPS5nNpr2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230415U8uP2sOhQEqawbSv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Beni Rugs </h3><p>三家公司正在联合创造一个慈善捐赠性质的独家地毯系列 Beni Rugs，是一系列专门定制的公共编织摩洛哥地毯，目前正在线上拍卖行 Paddle8 展出，拍卖后款项的 10%将捐给慈善机构。</p><p>整个系列的灵感来自 Mark Rothko、JoanMiró 等孟菲斯运动中的代表性艺术家，以及 Beni Rugs 的联合发起人 Tiberio Lobo-Navia 的原创抽象画作。拍卖在 10 月 17 日至 31 日期间举行。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230501G3raWz0L9DSBxMYk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230508wDuOpJRmrcgUSaho.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230511aB7QHnZf8tISlKXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230517AaMI52oWiBG4l3ZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230521cC4NmW3xb2KZSh6H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230528d1gsGtZFWC0afMXD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230529jFhM1LyckRvSr4UW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://paddle8.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Paddle8</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Pure Minimalist by Ameé Allsop</h3><p>澳洲建筑师、设计师 Ameé Allsop 推出了由漂白的美国白橡木和石灰华制成的极简主义家具系列 Pure Minimalist。出生于悉尼的 Ameé Allsop 称，整个系列的简洁线条、苍白色调和自然材料的色调，灵感都是源自 1950 年代后期的极简主义艺术运动，以及她在汉普顿家附近的海滩景观。</p><p>过去 12 年，她一直在悉尼和纽约做建筑师，Pure Minimalist 是她的第一个家具系列。她希望材料的美感和简单的结构比例成为这个系列的焦点。六件作品，包括俱乐部椅、餐桌、餐椅、嵌套咖啡桌、长凳和架子，均是在纽约手工制作而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230623X8GLbVIgYO2NDTjC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810252306309m3xGT0i7COlgI1Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810252306334G2dDNcviK5FtZk8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810252306434RCwNhbOBeLESt5I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499577\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230643oFRyUKw9PGCmYbOJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.ameeallsop.com/pure-minimalist/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ameé Allsop</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>See-Eat-Through by Aurore Brard</h3><p>埃因霍温设计学院的毕业生 Aurore Brard 创造了一系列色彩丰富的餐具 See-Eat-Through，旨在帮助有视力障碍的群体分辨食物和饮料的分量。See-Eat-Through 系列包括陶瓷盘子和碗，标有颜色带。水壶和水杯标有相似的颜色条带。另有一套带有触觉标记的餐具，使其更容易识别。</p><p>按照 Brard 的说法， See-Eat-Through 的设计目标是让视力低于 30％的人更容易发现物体。作为2018 年荷兰设计周的一部分，Brard 在埃因霍温设计许愿的研究生毕业展上展示了该项目，她希望为视障群体提供一套兼具功能性和审美吸引力的餐具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230737uURiIqNMhEVpjLDG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666244\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230739kHLI1v5MjFax96mn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667090\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810252307443kF5V6cv7PrIaKgN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666244\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181025230751tfBCwpqS3kHi2DLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666244\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/10/24/see-eat-through-tableware-visually-impaired-people-design-academy-eindhoven-aurore-brard/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></p>"}